author: Rachel Charlene Lewis
title: 8 birthday presents to buy this month that are just right for the Aquarius in your life
text:
8 birthday presents to buy this month that are just right for the Aquarius in your life It may be January, but that doesn’t mean the holiday shopping is over. Why? Because you’ve got January birthdays to shop for now, of course! If you’re on the hunt for the perfect gifts for January birthdays, and as obsessed with zodiac signs as we are , we’ve got you covered. These are just right for the Aquarius in your life, because these good-hearted thinkers deserve it.
And if you are an Aquarius, we won’t judge you if you want to grab one (or more!) of these goodies. Treat yourself, right? Right.
1. We absolutely dig this constellation mug and its swirling blues and purples ($18) Etsy For all of your coffee and tea drinking needs!
2. This pocket mirror is just right for the beauty-loving Aquarius ($5) Etsy To make sure you’re brows are ~on fleek~ 24/7.
3. This beautiful handmade wood art print featuring a glowing constellation ($40) Etsy One of these will add so much necessary pizazz to any living space.
4. This super chic zodiac mug is personalized, bright, and colorful ($14) Etsy It was already cute, but the customization pushes it to the top of our list!
5. This Aquarius elixir oil made with all natural essential oils and diluted with organic jojoba oil is so dreamy ($5) Etsy h, now this looks fun. We’re so curious about how this works!
6. This rad vintage Aquarius mug is just right for royalty ($24) Etsy We’re absolutely in love with this retro creation.
7. This crystal pendant features garnet , the January birth stone ($55) Etsy So gorgeous and unique!
8. This “Aquarius knows best” tee is all sass, and we heart it ($30) Etsy We hope you dig these gifts for January birthdays as much as we do! Happy gifting, friends.
